   "text": "What an American thinks about Indonesia."
  },
  {
   "start": 6.04,
   "end": 12.56,
   "text": "Indonesia is a very, very interesting place."
  },
  {
   "start": 13.02,
   "end": 14.2,
   "text": "It's a great place to travel."
  },
  {
   "start": 14.42,
   "end": 16.3,
   "text": "It's one of the most amazing places I've been to."
  },
  {
   "start": 17.02,
   "end": 20.48,
   "text": "Although it's a good place to travel as your first country to go to"
  },
  {
   "start": 20.48,
   "end": 22.86,
   "text": "If you haven't traveled for a while because they're really intense."
  },
  {
   "start": 25.24,
   "end": 26.74,
   "text": "Out of all the countries I've been to,"
  },
  {
   "start": 26.82,
   "end": 29.36,
   "text": "The most intense people are either going to be the Indonesians,"
  },
  {
   "start": 29.36,
   "end": 34.38,
   "text": "The Brazilians and the Moroccans as far as just like bubbling over with energy"
  },
  {
   "start": 34.38,
   "end": 37.02,
   "text": "And laughing and, you know."
  },
  {
   "start": 37.96,
   "end": 41.38,
   "text": "Like in Morocco, it's more about just getting in your face and being annoying."
  },
  {
   "start": 42.04,
   "end": 45.82,
   "text": "And in Brazil, they get like pissed off really easily."
  },
  {
   "start": 46.92,
   "end": 48.74,
   "text": "And, you know, they can be dangerous."
  },
  {
   "start": 49.0,
   "end": 52.48,
   "text": "But in Indonesia, they're just bubbly and, you know,"
  },
  {
   "start": 54.22,
   "end": 56.16,
   "text": "Laughing, ha-ha, and all that stuff."
  },
  {
   "start": 56.32,
   "end": 57.1,
   "text": "Freaking lots of energy."
  },
  {
   "start": 57.1,
   "end": 60.54,
   "text": "And the city and the towns, it's clean."
  },
  {
   "start": 60.74,
   "end": 62.1,
   "text": "Like they take care of their environment."
  },
  {
   "start": 63.02,
   "end": 63.26,
   "text": "They don't."
  },
  {
   "start": 63.98,
   "end": 65.7,
   "text": "One thing I forgot to say about Malaysia, though,"
  },
  {
   "start": 65.7,
   "end": 67.54,
   "text": "Is there's like lots of clear-cutting."
  },
  {
   "start": 67.7,
   "end": 69.72,
   "text": "And in Indonesia, there's no clear-cutting."
  },
  {
   "start": 70.2,
   "end": 72.26,
   "text": "And they're really poor in Indonesia, but, you know,"
  },
  {
   "start": 73.12,
   "end": 75.78,
   "text": "They paint their fences and all that stuff."
  },
  {
   "start": 76.74,
   "end": 77.28,
   "text": "It's cool."
  },
  {
   "start": 77.34,
   "end": 78.88,
   "text": "There's lots of different ethnic groups there."
  },
  {
   "start": 78.88,
   "end": 81.66,
   "text": "But, um, and I think their English is okay."
  },
  {
   "start": 82.16,
   "end": 92.21,
   "text": "I think their English is better in Indonesia than in, uh, than in, um, um,"
  },
  {
   "start": 93.11,
   "end": 94.47,
   "text": "Fucking flashback."
  },
  {
   "start": 94.99,
   "end": 99.25,
   "text": "Um, than in like, um, Nepal or, uh,"
  },
  {
   "start": 100.53,
   "end": 101.09,
   "text": "Thailand."
  },
  {
   "start": 101.09,
   "end": 101.33,
   "text": "Thailand."
  },
  {
   "start": 103.01,
   "end": 104.57,
   "text": "Damn, it's been so long, though."
  },
  {
   "start": 104.87,
   "end": 109.39,
   "text": "Um, but, um, well, actually, one place in Indonesia,"
  },
  {
   "start": 109.47,
   "end": 110.55,
   "text": "I didn't really like the locals."
  },
  {
   "start": 110.65,
   "end": 112.05,
   "text": "I was in Neos surf places."
  },
  {
   "start": 112.31,
   "end": 116.59,
   "text": "They were just, like, too aggressive and, uh, lie to you."
  },
  {
   "start": 116.87,
   "end": 117.79,
   "text": "Um, they do lie."
  },
  {
   "start": 118.05,
   "end": 119.27,
   "text": "They're big-time liars, though."
  },
  {
   "start": 119.47,
   "end": 121.29,
   "text": "Indonesians are big, big, big-time liars."
  },
  {
   "start": 121.45,
   "end": 123.11,
   "text": "More than any other place I've seen."
  },
  {
   "start": 124.49,
   "end": 126.99,
   "text": "Um, like one guy at a mosque, he told me he was, like,"
  },
  {
   "start": 126.99,
   "end": 128.85,
   "text": "He, like, was tour guide for Bill Clinton."
  },
  {
   "start": 129.13,
   "end": 130.29,
   "text": "And then he told me, like, you know,"
  },
  {
   "start": 130.35,
   "end": 132.51,
   "text": "I wasn't allowed to take a photo of the mosque."
  },
  {
   "start": 132.69,
   "end": 135.57,
   "text": "And then he said I had to pay, like, the guard."
  },
  {
   "start": 135.69,
   "end": 139.05,
   "text": "It was like, you have to pay him to get in."
  },
  {
   "start": 139.17,
   "end": 141.25,
   "text": "And, you know, that wasn't, found out it wasn't like that."
  },
  {
   "start": 141.43,
   "end": 144.19,
   "text": "And, like, just lots of other stuff."
  },
  {
   "start": 144.19,
   "end": 147.41,
   "text": "Like, this kid said he was, like, cousins with some other kid"
  },
  {
   "start": 147.41,
   "end": 148.67,
   "text": "At the surf place."
  },
  {
   "start": 148.69,
   "end": 149.69,
   "text": "And it turned out they weren't."
  },
  {
   "start": 150.73,
   "end": 153.51,
   "text": "They'll just, they'll just lie just because they like to lie."
  },
  {
   "start": 153.59,
   "end": 155.35,
   "text": "Kind of like Chileans."
  },
  {
   "start": 156.69,
   "end": 164.49,
   "text": "Um, and also, uh, um, but, um,"
  },
  {
   "start": 166.8,
   "end": 171.37,
   "text": "But they do want to hang out, hang out, hang out with you."
  },
  {
   "start": 172.29,
   "end": 173.09,
   "text": "If you pay."
  },
  {
   "start": 173.35,
   "end": 175.03,
   "text": "But, you know, they expect you to pay."
  },
  {
   "start": 175.09,
   "end": 176.57,
   "text": "But it doesn't really matter because it's so cheap."
  },
  {
   "start": 176.57,
   "end": 181.59,
   "text": "Um, but, uh, what else was I going to say?"
  },
  {
   "start": 181.81,
   "end": 186.13,
   "text": "Um, the spatial there is really, really, really crazy."
  },
  {
   "start": 186.27,
   "end": 188.43,
   "text": "Like, there's, there's no personal space there."
  },
  {
   "start": 188.53,
   "end": 191.79,
   "text": "Like, you know, I guess in Europe there's less personal space"
  },
  {
   "start": 191.79,
   "end": 192.35,
   "text": "Than in America."
  },
  {
   "start": 192.49,
   "end": 193.91,
   "text": "But in Indonesia there's, like, none."
  },
  {
   "start": 193.99,
   "end": 197.55,
   "text": "I remember I stayed in a, I was up on the big tower,"
  },
  {
   "start": 197.81,
   "end": 200.99,
   "text": "Lookout tower in Jakarta."
  },
  {
   "start": 200.99,
   "end": 204.13,
   "text": "Uh, and, um, I was waiting in line to get,"
  },
  {
   "start": 204.17,
   "end": 205.31,
   "text": "And there was, like, not many people,"
  },
  {
   "start": 205.45,
   "end": 206.73,
   "text": "Like six people in the whole room"
  },
  {
   "start": 206.73,
   "end": 209.81,
   "text": "To get in a, I, I, uh, a, uh,"
  },
  {
   "start": 210.63,
   "end": 212.39,
   "text": "The, the elevator to come down."
  },
  {
   "start": 212.45,
   "end": 214.17,
   "text": "And I'm waiting in there, and this kid,"
  },
  {
   "start": 214.59,
   "end": 216.63,
   "text": "This, like, teenage kid walks behind me,"
  },
  {
   "start": 217.15,
   "end": 217.61,
   "text": "Standing in line."
  },
  {
   "start": 217.91,
   "end": 221.13,
   "text": "I swear to God, presses his entire body up against me."
  },
  {
   "start": 221.31,
   "end": 223.59,
   "text": "Completely, completely, completely pressed up against me."
  },
  {
   "start": 223.59,
   "end": 224.55,
   "text": "And I look behind him,"
  },
  {
   "start": 225.03,
   "end": 228.01,
   "text": "And there's, like, nobody in the room."
  },
  {
   "start": 228.01,
   "end": 230.17,
   "text": "There's plenty of room to be waiting."
  },
  {
   "start": 231.03,
   "end": 232.05,
   "text": "And I look right at him,"
  },
  {
   "start": 232.13,
   "end": 233.59,
   "text": "And I look at his friend who's, like,"
  },
  {
   "start": 233.85,
   "end": 235.31,
   "text": "A guest standing right next to him."
  },
  {
   "start": 236.15,
   "end": 237.55,
   "text": "To, to, just to be, like,"
  },
  {
   "start": 237.77,
   "end": 239.29,
   "text": "What are you doing?"
  },
  {
   "start": 239.41,
   "end": 241.95,
   "text": "And they both had this, like,"
  },
  {
   "start": 242.03,
   "end": 243.19,
   "text": "Blank look on their face,"
  },
  {
   "start": 243.23,
   "end": 244.85,
   "text": "And then all the, the other people in there"
  },
  {
   "start": 244.85,
   "end": 246.09,
   "text": "Had a blank look on their face."
  },
  {
   "start": 246.11,
   "end": 247.51,
   "text": "And I realized that it was just, like,"
  },
  {
   "start": 247.53,
   "end": 248.61,
   "text": "A regular thing to do."
  },
  {
   "start": 248.69,
   "end": 251.61,
   "text": "Like, they just pack up, like, sardines,"
  },
  {
   "start": 251.67,
   "end": 252.65,
   "text": "Even if you don't have to."
  },
  {
   "start": 252.65,
   "end": 253.57,
   "text": "They're just used to it."
  },
  {
   "start": 253.73,
   "end": 255.59,
   "text": "And, you know, like, getting in the bus,"
  },
  {
   "start": 255.67,
   "end": 256.57,
   "text": "Getting in the big boat,"
  },
  {
   "start": 257.63,
   "end": 260.87,
   "text": "They all, that's how it was."
  },
  {
   "start": 260.91,
   "end": 262.91,
   "text": "Like, people just swarm around"
  },
  {
   "start": 262.91,
   "end": 265.41,
   "text": "In this big, like, mob of people,"
  },
  {
   "start": 265.57,
   "end": 266.91,
   "text": "And they just pack into the boat,"
  },
  {
   "start": 267.01,
   "end": 268.15,
   "text": "Just kind of haphazardly."
  },
  {
   "start": 268.31,
   "end": 269.99,
   "text": "And, and they didn't even bother"
  },
  {
   "start": 269.99,
   "end": 271.35,
   "text": "To open up the door all the way"
  },
  {
   "start": 271.35,
   "end": 272.15,
   "text": "Before they get in."
  },
  {
   "start": 272.19,
   "end": 273.49,
   "text": "And then they couldn't even continue"
  },
  {
   "start": 273.49,
   "end": 274.41,
   "text": "To open up the door."
  },
  {
   "start": 275.87,
   "end": 276.83,
   "text": "And they'd just be, like,"
  },
  {
   "start": 276.87,
   "end": 278.27,
   "text": "Climbing over this one door,"
  },
  {
   "start": 279.11,
   "end": 279.75,
   "text": "Drop down."
  },
  {
   "start": 279.75,
   "end": 282.35,
   "text": "But I think, and then, like,"
  },
  {
   "start": 282.35,
   "end": 284.15,
   "text": "Yeah, it's, like, really chaotic, too."
  },
  {
   "start": 284.25,
   "end": 286.19,
   "text": "Like, really chaotic, man."
  },
  {
   "start": 286.29,
   "end": 289.45,
   "text": "Like, I tried to get a ticket for a bus,"
  },
  {
   "start": 289.59,
   "end": 292.59,
   "text": "For a boat, on a bed,"
  },
  {
   "start": 292.71,
   "end": 294.09,
   "text": "And they said that they were sold out."
  },
  {
   "start": 294.15,
   "end": 294.97,
   "text": "So I go on the boat,"
  },
  {
   "start": 295.05,
   "end": 295.95,
   "text": "So I had to buy, like,"
  },
  {
   "start": 296.15,
   "end": 298.13,
   "text": "The ticket where you don't have a seat,"
  },
  {
   "start": 298.21,
   "end": 299.65,
   "text": "So you have to sleep, like, on the deck,"
  },
  {
   "start": 300.37,
   "end": 301.57,
   "text": "Or in the hallways,"
  },
  {
   "start": 301.61,
   "end": 303.05,
   "text": "Or, like, on the stairwell,"
  },
  {
   "start": 303.93,
   "end": 305.35,
   "text": "Where, like, all these people were."
  },
  {
   "start": 305.35,
   "end": 306.65,
   "text": "Like, if you walk up the stairs,"
  },
  {
   "start": 306.75,
   "end": 309.11,
   "text": "You have to step up and around"
  },
  {
   "start": 309.11,
   "end": 310.05,
   "text": "Over people"
  },
  {
   "start": 310.05,
   "end": 311.95,
   "text": "Because there's people sleeping"
  },
  {
   "start": 311.95,
   "end": 312.71,
   "text": "In the stairwell"
  },
  {
   "start": 312.71,
   "end": 314.01,
   "text": "And the hallway and stuff"
  },
  {
   "start": 314.01,
   "end": 315.61,
   "text": "And on the deck of the boat."
  },
  {
   "start": 317.25,
   "end": 318.93,
   "text": "But then I looked in the room"
  },
  {
   "start": 318.93,
   "end": 321.23,
   "text": "Where they said it was sold out"
  },
  {
   "start": 321.23,
   "end": 323.13,
   "text": "While, I swear to God,"
  },
  {
   "start": 323.25,
   "end": 326.09,
   "text": "While we're floating down the sea"
  },
  {
   "start": 326.09,
   "end": 329.53,
   "text": "And there's nobody in there."
  },
  {
   "start": 329.53,
   "end": 333.45,
   "text": "Like, hundreds of beds completely empty"
  },
  {
   "start": 333.45,
   "end": 334.77,
   "text": "Because, I guess,"
  },
  {
   "start": 334.81,
   "end": 336.03,
   "text": "The people who bought the tickets"
  },
  {
   "start": 336.03,
   "end": 337.57,
   "text": "Didn't want to pay the extra"
  },
  {
   "start": 337.57,
   "end": 338.49,
   "text": "For that berth,"
  },
  {
   "start": 338.67,
   "end": 340.23,
   "text": "So they paid the cheap version,"
  },
  {
   "start": 340.37,
   "end": 341.29,
   "text": "Which was only, like, three bucks"
  },
  {
   "start": 341.29,
   "end": 342.35,
   "text": "For, like, a day ride."
  },
  {
   "start": 342.41,
   "end": 342.85,
   "text": "It was crazy."
  },
  {
   "start": 344.11,
   "end": 348.67,
   "text": "And, um, and, uh,"
  },
  {
   "start": 349.65,
   "end": 350.81,
   "text": "But why did they tell me"
  },
  {
   "start": 350.81,
   "end": 352.57,
   "text": "That those other ones were sold out?"
  },
  {
   "start": 352.63,
   "end": 353.33,
   "text": "That was really weird."
  },
  {
   "start": 354.55,
   "end": 356.71,
   "text": "Um, but, uh,"
  },
  {
   "start": 357.83,
   "end": 359.09,
   "text": "But, yeah, they're really friendly."
  },
  {
   "start": 359.45,
   "end": 361.49,
   "text": "Like, I was up in the bar"
  },
  {
   "start": 361.49,
   "end": 362.67,
   "text": "And there was this kid there"
  },
  {
   "start": 362.67,
   "end": 363.49,
   "text": "Just babbling,"
  },
  {
   "start": 364.71,
   "end": 365.55,
   "text": "Like, laughing,"
  },
  {
   "start": 365.69,
   "end": 366.67,
   "text": "And everybody would laugh"
  },
  {
   "start": 366.67,
   "end": 367.31,
   "text": "And he was, like,"
  },
  {
   "start": 367.39,
   "end": 369.35,
   "text": "He was, like, acting totally goofy"
  },
  {
   "start": 369.35,
   "end": 371.63,
   "text": "And jumping around"
  },
  {
   "start": 371.63,
   "end": 372.77,
   "text": "And, uh, you know,"
  },
  {
   "start": 373.39,
   "end": 374.59,
   "text": "Way more,"
  },
  {
   "start": 374.67,
   "end": 375.95,
   "text": "It's kind of like Jim Carrey,"
  },
  {
   "start": 376.03,
   "end": 377.07,
   "text": "Like, everybody down there"
  },
  {
   "start": 377.07,
   "end": 378.13,
   "text": "Is Jim Carrey"
  },
  {
   "start": 378.13,
   "end": 379.19,
   "text": "And if you're acting like that"
  },
  {
   "start": 379.19,
   "end": 379.77,
   "text": "And then you're, like,"
  },
  {
   "start": 379.87,
   "end": 380.79,
   "text": "Cool, it was pretty cool."
  },
  {
   "start": 381.37,
   "end": 382.51,
   "text": "He invited me over to their place"
  },
  {
   "start": 382.51,
   "end": 384.05,
   "text": "But, and it landed"
  },
  {
   "start": 384.05,
   "end": 385.03,
   "text": "But I didn't go."
  },
  {
   "start": 386.33,
   "end": 390.62,
   "text": "Um, and, uh,"
  },
  {
   "start": 392.16,
   "end": 392.64,
   "text": "Yeah,"
  },
  {
   "start": 392.64,
   "end": 393.38,
   "text": "And there's this,"
  },
  {
   "start": 394.1,
   "end": 395.16,
   "text": "And there's this, uh,"
  },
  {
   "start": 397.63,
   "end": 398.93,
   "text": "There's this really"
  },
  {
   "start": 398.93,
   "end": 399.73,
   "text": "A distinct smell"
  },
  {
   "start": 399.73,
   "end": 400.65,
   "text": "That they have there too"
  },
  {
   "start": 400.65,
   "end": 401.55,
   "text": "Because they all smoke"
  },
  {
   "start": 401.55,
   "end": 402.15,
   "text": "Glove cigarettes"
  },
  {
   "start": 402.15,
   "end": 402.89,
   "text": "Instead of, uh,"
